The file anil_terraform_credentials.csv is not checkedin
* Steps used to create the credentials
    * login to aws console
    * choose IAM
        * create users
            * Username : anil_terraform
            * Tick : Generate key for the users
            * copy & download the keys
        * Give anil_terraform user Admin rights
            * Select the user
            * Click on Permissions --> Attach Policy
                * Selct AdministrativeAccess policy


